{"type": "article", "id": 2225, "title": "软陶榨汁机", "description": "", "date": "2014-09-07T23:03:49Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 2, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 7, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605222257NVWoCrbRniz5XTf2.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t<span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">通常情况下，我们看到的榨汁机都是塑料或者金属材质，而意大利设计师 Jacopo Ferrari 则为我们带来了一款软陶材质的榨汁机 Squeezer ，处处透出古典的味道。中间的彩色橡胶圈将上下两部分连结起来，在压榨橙子或柠檬的时候，上方未上釉的部分还能缓慢地吸收果汁的香气。整个榨汁机的制作过程均由手工完成，目前正在 </span><a href=\"https://launchbox.cutandpaste.com/projects/538f90f669702d7c5c0d0100\" target=\"_blank\">launchbox</a><span style=\"line-height:1.5;\"> 上进行众筹。</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726135110rCQhqTS0fvYJpXHE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726135111VZF8tGuQ0OCl4rHx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}